################ ATL - Animation and Transform language ##################

# The transform statement creates a transform that can be supplied as part of an at clause.

# Name must be a python identifier . eg-bounce1D etc.

# The tranform created by the ATL block is bound to this name.

# The xalign , yalign you see in the indented block is as per the alignment of characters in the game.


########## DANCE SPIRIT TRANSFORM ##########
transform bounce1D :
      xalign -0.01 yalign 0.8
      linear 0.17 yalign 0.2
      linear 0.3 yalign 0.8
      repeat
transform bounce2D :
      xalign -0.01 yalign 0.8
      linear 0.18 yalign 0.3
      linear 0.1 yalign 0.8
      repeat
transform bounce3D :
      xalign -0.01 yalign 0.8
      linear 0.3 yalign 0.3
      linear 0.17 yalign 0.9
      repeat

